videos.description: Tyler Herro  freezes the defense and takes the ball to the hoop to score the underhanded layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Herro takes the open lane for the layup) 2021/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herro takes the open lane for the layup

videos.description: Joel Embiid intercepts a bad pass then scores with a contested jumper on the other end of the court.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid with the steal and the bucket) 2021/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid with the steal and the bucket

videos.description: Coming off of a steal by Gabe Vincent, Duncan Robinson crosses the defense and floats in for the bucket.
videos.headline: Robinson shakes 2 Sixers defenders

videos.description: Ben Simmons hauls in the offensive rebound and goes up strong as he smashes down the rim-rattler.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Simmons gets his second bucket with a slam) 2021/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons gets his second bucket with a slam

videos.description: Before getting trapped, Ben Simmons dishes a quick pass to an open Danny Green, who knocks down his ninth 3-pointer of the game.
videos.headline: Green splashes career-best 9th triple

videos.description: Gabe Vincent brushes off the defense just enough to take the step-back jumper while drawing a foul on Ben Simmons.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Vincent makes off-balanced shot for and-1 bucket) 2021/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vincent makes off-balanced shot for and-1 bucket

videos.description: Tyler Herro lobs the ball over Joel Embiid, and Precious Achiuwa slams it down with two hands.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Herro, Achiuwa connect for the alley-oop) 2021/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herro, Achiuwa connect for the alley-oop

videos.description: Joel Embiid takes the inbound pass and knocks down the contested shot over Precious Achiuwa to tie the game late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid ties things up with a fadeaway jumper) 2021/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid ties things up with a fadeaway jumper

videos.description: Joel Embiid scores 45 points, including a perfect 13-of-13 from the free throw line, and hauls in 16 rebounds to lead the 76ers to a 137-134 win over the Heat.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Embiid scores 45 points in OT win over Miami) 2021/01/12 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Embiid scores 45 points in OT win over Miami
